attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: This East Side two family home will not disappoint! Completely rebuilt and meticulously maintained by the current owner, this property is ideal for investors looking to add a turnkey rental to their portfolio or an owner occupant collecting rent to help with the mortgage. Highly desirable part of South Boston in close proximity to the Seaport, downtown Boston and tons of shops and restaurants. The first floor features a mint 1 bedroom, 1 bath apartment with an open floor plan, gleaming hardwood floors, granite counters, and a private back patio. Upstairs you'll find a very spacious 3 bedroom, 2 full bath apartment featuring two floors of living, hardwoods throughout and a private back deck. Both units have updated central heat and AC. This property is very low maintenance and has an excellent rental history. Schedule a tour today!
